{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertmessage"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSAlertMessage","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Dialogs"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["        \/\/ A basic positive alert message with text and description","        OUDSAlertMessage(label: \"Label\", description: \"You should read this text\")","        \/\/ From a localizable in a bundle","        OUDSAlertMessage(LocalizedStringKey(\"label_wording\"), bundle: Bundle.module)","","        \/\/ With a rich text for the description (e.g. markdown here, do not forget to manage the errors)","        let richDescription = AttributedString(markdown: \"You **must read this text**\")","        OUDSAlertMessage(label: \"Label\", description: richDescription)","","        \/\/ A more complex alert message for warning status with a description and a close action","        \/\/ to dismiss the message.","        OUDSAlertMessage(label: \"Warning\", status: .warning, description: \"Some details about the warning\") {","              \/\/ Do some stuff here to dismiss the alert message when clicked","        }","","        \/\/ Add a custom icon for accent and neutral status","        OUDSAlertMessage(label: \"Label\", status: .accent(icon: OUDSIcon(asset: Image(\"ic_heart\"))))","        OUDSAlertMessage(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: OUDSIcon(asset: Image(\"ic_heart\"))))","","        \/\/ Add a custom action (i.e Link) at bottom (could also at top trailing position)","        @Environment(\\.openURL) private var openUrl","        let link = OUDSAlertMessage.Link(text: \"Action\", position: .bottom) {","           openUrl.callAsFunction(url)","        }","        OUDSAlertMessage(label: \"Label\", link: link)"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Rich text","anchor":"Rich-text"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Only the alert message description and bullet list can use rich text."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Strong text can be used sparingly within alert messages to highlight key information."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Underlined text must not be used for emphasis, as it is commonly associated with links."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If a hyperlink is needed within the content, the underlined style should be used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Italic should be used with care, some brands do not allow it like Orange brand."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No other text styles should be used."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Always check the results of rich text mode with high contrast, light and dark modes, and Voice Over vocalization."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-alert-message","isActive":true}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_alertMessage_Orange"}]},{"type":"